A Connection is a link between a Wallet and a Sales Channel.
## Connection Model

{% properties %}
  {% property name="id" type="string" %}
    The unique identifier of the Connection.
  {% /property %}

  {% property name="createdBy" type="crn" %}
    The User or API Key that created the Connection.
  {% /property %}

  {% property name="createdByAccountName" type="string" %}
  The name of the Account that created the Connection.
  {% /property %}

  {% property name="createdAt" type="timestamp" %}
    When the Connection was created.
  {% /property %}

  {% property name="status" type="string" %}
    The status of the Connection.
  {% /property %}

  {% property name="url" type="string" %}
    The url of the Connection.
  {% /property %}

  {% property name="merchantId" type="string" %}
    The [Merchant](/api/merchants/) the Connection is made on behalf of.
  {% /property %}

  {% property name="test" type="boolean" %}
    `true` if the Connection is for testing purposes only.
  {% /property %}

{% /properties %}

